In the Czech Republic, we first want to learn this, before we focus more on foreign countries, says a forty-one-year-old manager in an interview with iDNES.cz.
How does the Transfer app work and who can benefit from it?
Download it and register for free.
Then you can enter the route and data, how big a package you can transport and how much you want for it.
